WHO   — The Interrogation — the game's signature mechanic — walk into a red gang member and the view zooms to a close-up where you grab and interrogate him for intel
WHAT  — the game's signature mechanic — walk into a red gang member and the view zooms to a close-up where you grab and interrogate him for intel
WHERE — WBM · Wrath of the Black Manta — A.I Co. / Taito, NES 1990  Framework inputs: Wrath of the Black Manta; the Black Manta; DRAT; El Toro; the kidnapped children  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It is the famous novelty: the one mechanic everyone remembers, and the one that almost never works — a goon shrugs, says it's none of your business, and you let him go.
